Possibly:
Hynson, George B. — Progressive Candidate for Governor of Delaware, 1912.  Presumably the same person as wrote words for the Delaware state song, &quot;Our Delaware&quot;

<a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=50zwZmnf01IC&amp;pg=PA215&amp;lpg=PA215">books.google.com/books?id=50zwZmnf01IC&amp;pg=PA215&amp;l...</a> indicates that the author of &quot;Our Delaware&quot; is George Beswick Hynson, lawyer, publisher, and poet.  Some LoC catalog records give 1862 as his date of birth.
